{"text": "This modern 3-room apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building in Žilina offers stunning views of the Little Fatra and Martinky, including Vlčince. The layout is ideal for those seeking a high-quality living experience with ample storage space. The apartment features an east-facing living room with kitchen, providing beautiful vistas of the Žilina basin mountains. The bedroom is north-facing, preventing overheating and eliminating the need for air conditioning in summer months. The bathroom has a bidet shower by the toilet, underfloor electric heating, and a washing machine/dryer. The apartment is fully furnished and equipped with high-quality materials, including a brick cellar with ventilation system. The price of the property is 292000 €."}
